{"3282110": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "小咲: 狂怒之軌", "steam_appid": 3282110, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "dlc": [3305320], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282110/extras/b9b5ba3f1a1f5f96071de3eaf5a363ff.avif?t=1769528345\" width=800 height=282 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💥<strong><i>小咲是兇猛的鮫少女，也是外星帝國的高級將領。你將與她一起，踏上征服地球的狂野之旅！</i></strong>💥</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282110/extras/2031a23311ae64e4229c5d9f8482669f.poster.avif?t=1769528345\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282110/extras/2031a23311ae64e4229c5d9f8482669f.webm?t=1769528345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282110/extras/2031a23311ae64e4229c5d9f8482669f.mp4?t=1769528345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟小咲有一套獨特的訓練方法：在軌道上飛馳，將自己的部下觸手魔獸當作練習對象和肉盾。控制小咲，體驗高速飛奔的快感，同時消滅那些可憐的觸手魔獸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟等等，還有一個精彩的反轉！一位英勇的觸手魔獸隊長受夠了小咲的嗜血殘暴，決定發動政變，這在她的母艦上引發了巨大騷亂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟現在，你要幫助小咲在精心設計的軌道關卡中追捕叛變的觸手魔獸。不斷升級，躲避障礙，給叛徒一個永生難忘的慘痛教訓！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282110/extras/e3b8f8fe370a1c956c3ca6ce2183cf0a.poster.avif?t=1769528345\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282110/extras/e3b8f8fe370a1c956c3ca6ce2183cf0a.webm?t=1769528345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282110/extras/e3b8f8fe370a1c956c3ca6ce2183cf0a.mp4?t=1769528345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟不只如此！你還可以根據自己的喜好為小咲定制服裝。需要休息一下嗎？那就去互動按摩室放鬆恢復，然後再投入激烈的戰鬥吧。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>你要奪命狂奔，不斷升級，釋放小咲的怒火。準備好了嗎？追逐戰現在開始！</i></strong></h2>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282110/extras/b9b5ba3f1a1f5f96071de3eaf5a363ff.avif?t=1769528345\" width=800 height=282 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💥<strong><i>小咲是兇猛的鮫少女，也是外星帝國的高級將領。你將與她一起，踏上征服地球的狂野之旅！</i></strong>💥</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282110/extras/2031a23311ae64e4229c5d9f8482669f.poster.avif?t=1769528345\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282110/extras/2031a23311ae64e4229c5d9f8482669f.webm?t=1769528345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282110/extras/2031a23311ae64e4229c5d9f8482669f.mp4?t=1769528345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟小咲有一套獨特的訓練方法：在軌道上飛馳，將自己的部下觸手魔獸當作練習對象和肉盾。控制小咲，體驗高速飛奔的快感，同時消滅那些可憐的觸手魔獸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟等等，還有一個精彩的反轉！一位英勇的觸手魔獸隊長受夠了小咲的嗜血殘暴，決定發動政變，這在她的母艦上引發了巨大騷亂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟現在，你要幫助小咲在精心設計的軌道關卡中追捕叛變的觸手魔獸。不斷升級，躲避障礙，給叛徒一個永生難忘的慘痛教訓！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282110/extras/e3b8f8fe370a1c956c3ca6ce2183cf0a.poster.avif?t=1769528345\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282110/e